{"tid":1397911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地好需要遠攻（遊戲攻略)","createTime":"2019-08-02T15:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T14:05:38.000Z","uid":82067,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"da8378265cf543627c3be2a371591a7183469368","tid":1397911,"uid":82067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hhhHecSt3LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhhhHecSt3LM&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=8caa2690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hhhHecSt3LM</a><br />\n幾時行軍佈陣，幾時都係先用遠攻屈人地嘅兵先，得人地攻到黎前線時先減弱士氣同兵力，然後先用前線頂。所以我覺得有效制衡敵人，必先要有相應嘅弓手，甚至投石器。<br />\n當然呢個遊戲仲有好多戰術可以講啦，歡迎各位戰術撚討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f78587762084f8587680912e6a4437bb3234769","tid":1397911,"uid":82067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"屌，出左去時事台，仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我打機咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b88dd8fac2ab1a93af49e6fb8f18afe92f9111c","tid":1397911,"uid":65981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"打機學術討論<br />\n親身試過合成 氣球加樽蓋嗰個嘢唔係好掂<br />\nCd長 距離唔可以遠 大耐得幾米<br />\n而且用多幾次彈力開始差 唔多建議整<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打可以淘到丫差仲掂 彈力同射距都強<br />\n可以突襲一下<br />\n<br />